      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
 
      ** Convert file fields into screen format
 
     C                   EXSR      SRPROC
 
     C                   RETURN
 
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  SRPROC - Convert file fields into screen format              *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called by: Main                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *  Calls    : LELOAMCVT, ZASETINCVT                             *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
     C     SRPROC        BEGSR
 
     C                   EVAL      TRANSDTL = *BLANKS
     C                   EVAL      DDACTN = PACTN
 
      ** Convert Loan Amendment to screen format
     C                   CALLB     'LELOAMCVT'
 
     C                   PARM      *BLANKS       RetCodeOut
 
      ***  Loan amendment in file format
     C                   PARM                    LOAMFilFmt
 
      * Date format indicator
     C                   PARM                    BJDFIN
      *
      * OUTPUTS
      *
      * Loan Amendment details in screen format
     C                   PARM                    LOAMScnFmt
 
      *
      ***  Output only screen field : Loan status
     C                   PARM                    DDSTAT           16
     C                   PARM                    LOAMFilXFmt                                  CRE073
      *
      **  Add the action code
     C                   MOVE      PACTN         DDACTN
 
     C                   IF        RetCodeOut <> *Blanks
     C                   EVAL      RetCodeIn = '*ERROR'
     C                   ELSE
 
     C                   EVAL      TRANSDTL = LOAMScnFmt
 
     C                   ENDIF
 
     C                   ENDSR
 
      *****************************************************************
      /EJECT
      *****************************************************************
      *                                                               *
      *  *INZSR - Program Initialisation routine                      *
      *                                                               *
      *  Called by: Implicitly on program activation                  *
      *                                                               *
      *  Calls    : None                                              *
      *                                                               *
      *****************************************************************
 
     C     *INZSR        BEGSR
 
     C     *ENTRY        PLIST
 
      ** INPUT
      ** =====
 
      ** Return Code
     C                   PARM                    RetCodeIn
 
      ** Action code
     C                   PARM                    PACTN
 
      ** Midas LE valid loan amendments file record
     C                   PARM                    LOAMFilFmt
 
      * Date format indicator
     C                   PARM                    BJDFIN            1
 
      ** OUTPUT
      ** ======
 
      ** Data Replication Details Screen Format
     C                   PARM                    TRANSDTL
     C                   PARM                    LOAMFilXFmt                                  CRE073
 
